Flow.Name: ECU_Ignition_Shut_Off_Request
Flow.Description: This information indicates that the ECU has requested an ignition shut off to kill the engine.

Flow.Name: Mechanical_Drivetrain_Engaged
Flow.Description: information indicating that the mechanical drivetrain is engaged (which means the clutch is engaged and the gear position is not neutral)

Flow.Name: Ctrl_Motor_Starter_Relay
Flow.Description: This is the control (not the power) of the starter relay
